

We benchmarked the BPI M3 against the current 500 gorillia, the [Raspberry Pi 2](https://www.raspberrypi.org/products/raspberry-pi-2-model-b/). 

First up the weigh in:

| Metric | Raspbery Pi 2 Model B | BPI M3 |
| CPU Model  |  ARM Cortex-A7 | ARM A83T | 
| CPU Speed  |  900MHz | 2GHz | 
| Core Count |  4  | 8 |
| RAM        |  1GB | 2GB | 
| Ethernet   | 100Mb/s | 1000Mb/s | 
| Cost  | [$37.61](http://amzn.to/1ROanST) | [$75](http://amzn.to/1ROaCNA) |


   